Stephenson, Neal

The Big U

New York: Random House, 1984. First Edition. Paperback. First edition of his first book, a trade paperback original. Never reprinted. Nice copy with tiny red remainder mark to bottom edge. Minor small crease to back top corner. Scarce book by the author of SnowCrash. Near Fine. Item #000697
